insert into cars (make, color, model, price, year, details) values ('Mercedez', 'Yellow', 'R3', 100000, 2015,"Introducing the extraordinary Mercedez Benz R3, a pinnacle of automotive innovation and luxury. Engineered with passion and precision, this futuristic masterpiece surpasses all expectations. Step into a world of unparalleled elegance, where sleek lines seamlessly blend with aerodynamic curves, showcasing its captivating exterior design. The Mercedez Benz R3 boasts an advanced hybrid engine, delivering an unrivaled combination of power and efficiency, ensuring a thrilling and eco-conscious driving experience.");
